# Flutter/Dart/Pub related (Flutter가 하위 폴더로 이동해도 적용되도록 ** 사용)
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
**/.dart_tool/
**/.flutter-plugins
**/.flutter-plugins-dependencies
**/.pub-cache/
**/.pub/
**/build/

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Android Studio will place build artifacts here (Flutter)
**/android/app/debug/
**/android/app/profile/
**/android/app/release/

# Installers / downloaded binaries (never commit)
*.msi
*.exe
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.tgz

# Local maintenance scripts (do not commit)
reorg.ps1
